    <question>
        <prompt>Who was Hiram Revels?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">First African American U.S. Senator</option>
            <option letter="b">Leader of the Freedmen's Bureau</option>
            <option letter="c">Confederate general</option>
            <option letter="d">Radical Republican leader</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>Hiram Revels became the first African American U.S. Senator in 1870, representing Mississippi in the seat previously held by Jefferson Davis.</explanation>
